#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Properties Tab"
msgstr "Savybių skirtukas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can refine your search. These are the special refinements you can "
"choose:"
msgstr ""
"Čia galite dar labiau detalizuoti paiešką. Galite naudoti tokius "
"patikslinimus:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all files created or modified"
msgstr "Rasti visus failus, sukurtus ar pakeistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can either enter two dates, between which the files were created or "
"modified, or specify a time period."
msgstr ""
"Paieškos rezultatuose bus rodomi tik tie failai, kurie buvo sukurti ar "
"modifikuoti tarp nurodytų dviejų datų."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "File size is"
msgstr "Failo dydis yra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here you can specify if the file has to be at least or as most as big as "
